# Copy this file to `skyportal_token` (same directory) and replace the contents
# with a SkyPortal System admin token. The file must contain only the token id,
# no "token " prefix and no trailing newline is required.
#
# Generate one from an admin account via the API, or reuse the INITIAL_ADMIN
# token written to .tokens.yaml on first server startup.
#
# `skyportal_token` is gitignored so the secret is never committed.
REPLACE_WITH_A_SYSTEM_ADMIN_TOKEN
